    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 200°C/ 180°C (fan)/ gas 6</p><p>Boil a kettle</p><p>Chop the <strong>paneer</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
